OL,3,CThousands living in 'absolute poverty'
OL,4,Cin County Durham
OL,6,FAround one in five people in are
OL,7,Fliving in 'absolute poverty' and rely
OL,8,Fon incentives and reductions on their
OL,9,Fbills to get by.
OL,11,FFigures from Durham County Council
OL,12,Festimate that over 112,000 people in
OL,13,Fthe authority area struggle to live
OL,14,Fwithout extra support.
OL,16,FIt comes as the gap between County
OL,17,FDurham and England has widened in
OL,18,Frecent years.
