OL,3,CThousands living in 'absolute poverty'
OL,4,Cin County Durham
OL,6,FIn Durham in the year up to 31 October
OL,7,F2022, there was a 65% rise in the
OL,8,Fnumber of residents in the county
OL,9,Fgetting food and fuel vouchers, with
OL,10,F17,000 food vouchers and 3,100 fuel
OL,11,Fvouchers were issued.
OL,13,FFurthermore, the number of people in
OL,14,Fwork but claiming Universal Credit
OL,15,Fmore than doubled from 9,500 in March
OL,16,F2020 to 19,900 in September 2023.
