OL,6,FAn estimated 17,000 people were also
OL,7,Fthought to have used the county's
OL,8,Fnetwork of Warm Spaces last year, with
OL,9,Fthe offer being broadened to include
OL,10,Fadvice services and relaunched as
OL,11,FWelcome Spaces.
OL,13,FMore than 53,500 are benefiting from
OL,14,Fthe Local Council Tax Reduction
OL,15,FScheme, with over 25,000 people
OL,16,Freceiving the maximum 100 percent
OL,17,Fdiscount.
