OL,6,FDiscussing the matter at a Durham
OL,7,FCounty Council cabinet meeting on
OL,8,FWednesday 14 February, Cllr Alan
OL,9,FShield said the council is "absolutely
OL,10,Fcommitted to supporting our most
OL,11,Fvulnerable residents" as part of its
OL,12,FPoverty Strategy and Action Plan.
OL,14,FThe councillor for Leadgate and
OL,15,FMedomsley said the risk of poverty and
OL,16,Fhardship across the county had
OL,17,Fincreased due to the rising cost of
OL,18,Fliving.
