OL,6,FHe continued: "We are seeing rising
OL,7,Fdemand for food banks, with more
OL,8,Fpeople in work using them, more
OL,9,Ffamilies struggling to get by and
OL,10,Fafford essential basics, and rising
OL,11,Fdebt problems.
OL,13,F"We're doing all we can to provide
OL,14,Fpeople with a safety net and a huge
OL,15,Fand ongoing local effort is going into
OL,16,Fthis, not just from ourselves but from
OL,17,Four public and voluntary sector
OL,18,Fpartners too.
