OL,6,F"Last financial year we helped 5,900
OL,7,Fnew service users claim around
OL,8,F#15.5million in income, and in the
OL,9,Fsecond and third quarters of this
OL,10,Ffinancial year we've helped 3,282 new
OL,11,Fservice users claim #7.7million.
OL,13,F"We've also introduced financial
OL,14,Finclusion support officers in some of
OL,15,Four secondary schools to offer
OL,16,Ffamilies money and debt management
OL,17,Fadvice and help them claim their full
OL,18,Fbenefits entitlements. Any extra
OL,19,Fincome we can find for people can be a
OL,20,Fmassive help to them."
